parameters:
Afterwards, upon returning from the former BB Gang's base,
Eliza summarized the situation and reported to the supreme
commander.

While skillfully deceiving about Black Cute and Pure Dark,
she exposed Guido's misdeeds. As a result, Guido was
stripped of his official authority, which was then
transferred entirely to Eliza.

Moreover, Guido, after his betrayal of the BB Gang was
discovered that evening, fled from the Justice Knights'
base. He has been missing ever since.

Rumors circulated for a while about hearing a voice similar
to Guido's from the new mysterious researcher's lab... but
Doctor Mad is the only one who knows the truth.

Furthermore, Eliza denounced the government's (mainly
Guido's) inhumane actions to the public. Of course, the
sexual content was omitted, but Pure Flame herself, becoming
somewhat of a government mascot, also supported Eliza. The
trust in the government was shaken at once.

Eliza seems to be planning to enter politics on this wave,
and she seems busy every day.

And so, Flare and the others returned to their daily
lives...
